un all tests in your project\n through miri.\n \n+## Running miri with full libstd\n+\n+Per default libstd does not contain the MIR of non-polymorphic functions.  When\n+miri hits a call to such a function, execution terminates.  To fix this, it is\n+possible to compile libstd with full MIR:\n+\n+```sh\n+cargo install xargo\n+cd xargo/\n+RUSTFLAGS='-Zalways-encode-mir' xargo build --target `rustc -vV | egrep '^host: ' | sed 's/^host: //'`\n+```\n+\n+Now you can run miri against the libstd compiled by xargo:\n+\n+```sh\n+cargo run --bin miri -- --sysroot ~/.xargo/HOST tests/run-pass/vecs.rs\n+```\n+\n+Notice that you will have to re-run the last step of the preparations above when\n+your toolchain changes (e.g., when you update the nightly).  Also, xargo doesn't\n+currently work with nightlies newer than 2017-04-23.\n+\n ## Contributing and getting help\n \n Check out the issues on this GitHub repository for some ideas. There's lots that"}, {"sha": "031ad9a8795491b7e05f2290d3063fa31ab808df", "filename": "xargo/Cargo.lock", "status": "added", "additions": 4, "deletions": 0, "changes": 4, "blob_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/blob/1ae01b422b7c961b35d2f70550f1f795464824a4/xargo%2FCargo.lock", "raw_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/raw/1ae01b422b7c961b35d2f70550f1f795464824a4/xargo%2FCargo.lock", "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/contents/xargo%2FCargo.lock?ref=1ae01b422b7c961b35d2f70550f1f795464824a4", "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,4 @@\n+[root]\n+name = \"miri-xargo\"\n+version = \"0.0.0\"\n+"}, {"sha": "9129c105b112bb1b3dd597b118e2ac13466b505b", "filename": "xargo/Cargo.toml", "status": "added", "additions": 6, "deletions": 0, "changes": 6, "blob_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/blob/1ae01b422b7c961b35d2f70550f1f795464824a4/xargo%2FCargo.toml", "raw_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/raw/1ae01b422b7c961b35d2f70550f1f795464824a4/xargo%2FCargo.toml", "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/contents/xargo%2FCargo.toml?ref=1ae01b422b7c961b35d2f70550f1f795464824a4", "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,6 @@\n+[package]\n+name = \"miri-xargo\"\n+description = \"A dummy project for building libstd with xargo.\"\n+version = \"0.0.0\"\n+\n+[dependencies]"}, {"sha": "32f45c4a9816ff58cf8bb929f7edc6c0687a3bd5", "filename": "xargo/Xargo.toml", "status": "added", "additions": 2, "deletions": 0, "changes": 2, "blob_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/blob/1ae01b422b7c961b35d2f70550f1f795464824a4/xargo%2FXargo.toml", "raw_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/raw/1ae01b422b7c961b35d2f70550f1f795464824a4/xargo%2FXargo.toml", "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/contents/xargo%2FXargo.toml?ref=1ae01b422b7c961b35d2f70550f1f795464824a4", "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,2 @@\n+[dependencies]\n+std = {features = [\"panic_unwind\", \"jemalloc\"]}"}, {"sha": "e69de29bb2d1d6434b8b29ae775ad8c2e48c5391", "filename": "xargo/src/lib.rs", "status": "added", "additions": 0, "deletions": 0, "changes": 0, "blob_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/blob/1ae01b422b7c961b35d2f70550f1f795464824a4/xargo%2Fsrc%2Flib.rs", "raw_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/raw/1ae01b422b7c961b35d2f70550f1f795464824a4/xargo%2Fsrc%2Flib.rs", "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/contents/xargo%2Fsrc%2Flib.rs?ref=1ae01b422b7c961b35d2f70550f1f795464824a4"}]}